<p>[2]Chandran Suja V , Barakat A I . A Mathematical Model for the Sounds Produced by Knuckle Cracking[J]. Scientific Reports, 2018, 8(1):4600. </p>
<p>[3]Unger D L . Does knuckle cracking lead to arthritis of the fingers?[J]. Arthritis &amp; Rheumatology, 1998, 41(5):949-950. </p>
<p>[4]Asad, Rizvi, Marios,等. Let's Get a Hand on this: Review of the Clinical Anatomy of "Knuckle Cracking".[J]. Clinical Anatomy, 2018. </p>
<p>[5]Deweber K , Olszewski M , Ortolano R . Knuckle Cracking and Hand Osteoarthritis[J]. Journal of the American Board of Family Medicine, 2011, 24(2):169-174. </p>
